beer.beer_description:
Little brother of the Husky Pale Ale. 
By adding the hops to the whirlpool at the last moment we maximised flavour and aroma yet reduced the bitterness to very low levels. 
With our low bitterness this is our most sessionable beer yet. 
At 1.1 standard drinks this golden ale is an excellent thirst quencher.
